Playing breakout by gesture.


EXECUTION ENVIRONMENT
=====================================
The codes were tested under Mac OS X 10.5.8 and Windows Vista, 
and it should be also working under Linux system.

EXTERNAL PACKAGE INCLUDED
=====================================
We are mainly focusing on visual interface, so the prototype of 
the game was borrowed from pybreakout, which can be downloaded 
from http://code.google.com/p/pybreakout/source/checkout

HOW TO INSTALL?
=====================================
You need python 2.5.1 (or newer version), OpenCV 2.1.


HOW TO RUN?
=====================================

Start the game:
  $ python main.py


